&lt;p&gt;先看wiki的定义：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A model is an informative representation of an object, person or system. The term originally denoted the plans of a building in late 16th-century English, and derived via French and Italian ultimately from Latin modulus, a measure&lt;/p&gt;
